<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 13:46:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>减肥药物的最新好处：提高睾酮和精子质量</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-latest-benefit-of-obesity-drugs-boosting-testosterone-and-sperm-quality</link><description>初步研究发现，服用 GLP-1 药物的人睾酮水平会增加或稳定。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-latest-benefit-of-obesity-drugs-boosting-testosterone-and-sperm-quality.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 13:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-latest-benefit-of-obesity-drugs-boosting-testosterone-and-sperm-quality</guid></item><item><title>心理学软件工具</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/psychology-software-tools</link><description>用于行为研究的最全面的刺激呈现软件。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/logo.psychology-software-tools2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 13:31:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/psychology-software-tools</guid></item><item><title>单个原子如何包含整个量子宇宙</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-a-single-atom-contains-the-entire-quantum-universe</link><description>通过在原子尺度或更小的尺度上探测宇宙，我们可以揭示整个标准模型，以及随之而来的量子宇宙。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/logo.how-a-single-atom-contains-the-entire-quantum-universe2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 13:16:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-a-single-atom-contains-the-entire-quantum-universe</guid></item><item><title>“没有人认为这是可能的。”一架太空望远镜正在从太空中坠落。这是美国宇航局拯救它的大胆计划</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/no-one-thought-it-was-going-to-be-possible-a-space-telescope-is-falling-out-of-space-this-is-nasas-daring-plan-to-save-it</link><description>美国宇航局的斯威夫特太空天文台正在脱离轨道。商业公司能在九个月内建造一艘宇宙飞船来拯救它吗？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/no-one-thought-it-was-going-to-be-possible-a-space-telescope-is-falling-out-of-space-this-is-nasas-daring-plan-to-save-it2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 02:33:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/no-one-thought-it-was-going-to-be-possible-a-space-telescope-is-falling-out-of-space-this-is-nasas-daring-plan-to-save-it</guid></item><item><title>如何为量子系统创建可区分的状态</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-to-create-distinguishable-states-for-quantum-systems</link><description>世界各地的研究人员正在竞相开发新的基于量子的传感、通信、计算和控制系统，这些系统有望超越传统系统。创建稳定、可测量、可区分的量子态是任何此类系统的核心，是一项艰巨的任务。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-to-create-distinguishable-states-for-quantum-systems.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 02:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-to-create-distinguishable-states-for-quantum-systems</guid></item><item><title>科学家开发可穿戴机器人系统以恢复手部功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-develop-wearable-robotic-system-to-restore-hand-function</link><description>维也纳医科大学的研究人员与苏黎世联邦理工学院、慕尼黑工业大学和贝尔格莱德医学院合作，开发了一种可穿戴神经机器人系统，将电神经刺激与手外骨骼相结合。在一项涉及 14 名因神经损伤导致手部损伤的患者的临床试验中，该技术支持手指活动、触觉感知和抓握控制。结果证明了个性化辅助系统对于患有脊髓或脑损伤的人们的潜力。该研究最近发表在《科学进展》杂志上。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-develop-wearable-robotic-system-to-restore-hand-function.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 02:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-develop-wearable-robotic-system-to-restore-hand-function</guid></item><item><title>接近绝对零时，该晶体管开始像脑细胞一样发挥作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/near-absolute-zero-this-transistor-starts-acting-like-a-brain-cell</link><description>一个像极寒状态下的脑细胞一样工作的晶体管可以帮助解锁下一代量子计算机和太空探索系统。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/near-absolute-zero-this-transistor-starts-acting-like-a-brain-cell.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 01:48:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/near-absolute-zero-this-transistor-starts-acting-like-a-brain-cell</guid></item><item><title>体内皮质树突的电压动态</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/voltage-dynamics-of-cortical-dendrites-in-vivo</link><description>对活体小鼠 2/3 层皮质神经元中的体细胞和树突进行同步电压成像，揭示了尖峰反向传播的丰富动态，其幅度由尖峰历史、树突位置和行为状态决定。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/voltage-dynamics-of-cortical-dendrites-in-vivo.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 01:33:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/voltage-dynamics-of-cortical-dendrites-in-vivo</guid></item><item><title>新的人工智能数学工具可以提高图像编辑、药物发现和模拟的能力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-ai-math-tool-could-sharpen-image-editing-drug-discovery-and-simulations</link><description>克拉克森大学的研究人员开发了一种新的数学工具，可以使人工智能系统在从图像编辑到药物发现等应用中更加准确、可控和有用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-ai-math-tool-could-sharpen-image-editing-drug-discovery-and-simulations.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 01:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-ai-math-tool-could-sharpen-image-editing-drug-discovery-and-simulations</guid></item><item><title>国际空间站大约每 90 分钟绕地球一周，但多年来没有任何美国航天器能够到达它——只有一家私营公司介入弥补了这一差距</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-international-space-station-orbits-earth-roughly-every-90-minutes-yet-for-years-no-american-spacecraft-could-reach-it-a-gap-a-single-private-company-stepped-in-to-close</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 01:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-international-space-station-